title: Fellowes® Powershred® 60Cs Cross-Cut Shredder Demo - UK
description:
Powershred® 60Cs Cross-Cut Shredder
Shreds 10 sheets per pass into 4x50mm cross-cut particles (Security Level P-3) 
Patented SafeSense® Technology stops shredding when hands touch the paper entry
22 litre bin with lift-off head
Shreds staples, paper clips and credit cards
For individual use

Find out more here:
http://www.fellowes.com/gb/en/Products/Pages/product-details.aspx?prod=UK-4606201
